Name: Rcbo
Product_Type: RCBO (Residual Current Circuit Breaker with Overcurrent Protection)
Specifications: Amperage: 6A ; Poles: TPN ; Breaking Capacity: 10kA ; Trip Curve: C ; Sensitivity: 100mA
Key_Features: Real Trip Indicator , Test Button For Device Health , Lockable Knob , Air Flow Channels , Functionally independent of line voltage , Mid trip dolly - Trip Indication , Bi-stable Easy Din -Clip helps for easy installation , IS/IEC Certified
Full_Description: Polycab RCBO (Residual current operated circuit breaker with overcurrent protection) provides protection against both ground faults and overcurrents in electrical circuits. RCBOs are used to enhance electrical safety by quickly interrupting the power supply when ground faults or overcurrents are detected, preventing electric shock, fire hazards, and equipment damage
Short_Description: Protection against earth faults, short-circuits, overload & leakage current
